 upon him, said, \u201cIslam has eight shares: Islam is a share, prayer is a share, charity is a share, Hajj pilgrimage to the House is a share, fasting is a share, enjoining good is a share, forbidding evil is a share, and\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32949,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/29\/islam-includes-wudu-ghusl\/","url_meta":{"origin":17315,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Wudu: Islam includes ablution, ritual purification","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 29, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: Gabriel said, \u201cO Muhammad, what is Islam?\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIslam is to testify there is no god but Allah and Muhammad is the Messenger of Allah, to pray, to give charity, to perform pilgrimage, to wash oneself of\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33359,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/09\/05\/ibn-umar-why-not-go-for-jihad\/","url_meta":{"origin":17315,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Islam: Ibn Umar, why do you not go for jihad?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 5, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Tawus reported: A man said to Abdullah ibn Umar, \u201cWhy do you not join the military campaigns?\u201d Ibn Umar said, \u201cI heard the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, say: Verily, Islam is built upon five: to testify t